race.comment: PRINCE LEVI (5) wasn't too far away in Saturday metro grade last time out and should find this assignment a touch easier. Ready to peak now fourth run from the spell and is sure to be right there when the judge calls a halt. TAPILDOODLEDO (1) has placed over this track and trip, draws the inside marble and gets a stack of weight relief with the 3kg claim. Plenty to like about his prospects. SIR LAMORAK (3) has a win and two seconds from seven attempts over this staying journey and will be rock-hard fit for this. Top-three candidate. TAJAWAL (2) gets the services of Maloney in the saddle and should be kept safe. FARWEST (7) has placed four of five over this trip and may earn some minor money.
